Welcome to the Q&A video for "Missing Value Imputation with Item Response Theory"! If you're looking to gain a deeper understanding of this topic, we highly recommend watching the talk by Allen Downey and Ricardo Vieira: 👉 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uyznG61myy0

In this Q&A session, Allen & Ricardo addresses various questions related to "Missing Value Imputation with Item Response Theory" providing further insights and clarifications.
